{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"01180aac05","title":"对订制军用雨衣被好商诈骗情况简报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b2c9fab366","index":0,"year":1951,"month":4,"day":26,"articleId":"01180aac05"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"eef8c50cfc","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"01180aac05","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中央人民政府最高人民检察院副检察长李六如1951年4月24日简报的批语。"},{"id":"941c522930","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"01180aac05","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李六如关于军委订制200万件军用雨衣被好商诈骗，国家财产遗受重大损失事件的简报说，此项雨衣是1950年10月至11月由华北军区后勤部代表军委后勤部通过中央轻工业部在北京、天津、青岛三地订制55万件，另由上海等地承制145万件。单就天津承制30万件说，由于好商预知订制雨衣之消息，并乘我军需急追即串通活动，大量拾高雨衣成本，致使国家财产损失近90亿元（人民币旧币）。如果按京、津、青三地订制55万件计算，国家损失140亿元（人民币旧币）以上：如果按全国订制200万件计算，国家损失更大。"}],"contents":[{"id":"41af29ae6d","type":"title","text":"对订制军用雨衣被好商诈骗情况简报的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"01180aac05"},{"id":"eef8c50cfc","type":"paragraph","text":"必须严格处理，教育干部。P","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"01180aac05"},{"id":"941c522930","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"01180aac05"},{"id":"54fa1ed209","type":"paragraph","text":"四月二十六日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"01180aac05"}],"page":{"id":"fe13b7f918","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"01180aac05","start":257,"end":257}}}},"__N_SSG":true}